     Syntax:   CHANOPT <channel> MOTD <message>
     Use:      Set a Messeg Of The Day, this will be dispalyed to users
               who are in the channel userlist and they have authed
     Example:  /msg \n CHANOPT #MyChan MOTD Meeting tonight at 7pm CST
     ----------
     Suggested Use:
     ----------
               Used to display messeges to channel members about channel 
               specific issues.
